OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fburning back to North Sea coasts
OL,7,Fduring the morning where it may
OL,8,Flinger. Very warm or hot again inland,
OL,9,Fbut cooler and fresher around the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe low cloud around the east
OL,13,Fcoast moving inland in places. Staying
OL,14,Fdry with the clear skies through the
OL,15,FTrossachs and west, winds remaining
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
