OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny low cloud should clear
OL,6,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Temperatures down a bit,
OL,8,Fbut still warm or very warm in any
OL,9,Fsunshine. Light northwest winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and settled, although a little
OL,13,Fearly light rain or drizzle possible
OL,14,Fover the hills. Cloudy or bright with
OL,15,Fsunny spells developing. Feeling warm
OL,16,Fin any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
